<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Introduction of KISTI Cats ヽ(=^･ω･^=)丿</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: #f5f5f5;
        }
        h1 {
            color: #333;
        }
        .cat-container {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(200px, 1fr));
            gap: 20px;
        }
        .cat {
            background-color: #ffffff;
            padding: 15px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            text-align: center;
            margin: 10px;
        }
        .cat img {
            max-width: 150px; /* Adjust this to the desired width */
            height: auto; /* Maintain aspect ratio */
            border-radius: 5px;
        }
        .cat p {
            color: #555;
            font-size: 14px;
        }
        a {
            text-decoration: none;
            color: #007bff;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <h1>Introduction Cats</h1>
    <div class="cat-container">
        <!-- Leon -->
        <div class="cat">
            <img src="./photos/leon2.JPG" alt="Cat 1">
            <p>The most adorable cat of KISTI.</p>
        </div>
        <!-- Milk cow -->
        <div class="cat">
            <img src="./photos/milk2.JPG" alt="Cat 2">
            <p>Jeotso(Milk cow) is so cute. He likes churrr a lot!!</p>
        </div>
        <!-- Lucy -->
        <div class="cat">
            <img src="./photos/lucy1.JPG" alt="Cat 3">
            <p>Lucy is Jeotso lover. Always follow him :)</p>
        </div>
        <!-- Leo -->
        <div class="cat">
            <img src="./photos/leo1.JPG" alt="Cat 4">
            <p>Leo is Leon's mom. She lives around her daughter, Leon.</p>
        </div>
        <!-- JJobso(Fake milk cow) -->
        <div class="cat">
            <img src="./photos/fake1.JPG" alt="Cat 4">
            <p>JJobso looks similar to the Jeotso but he/she is shy cat. He/She makes sound always!!</p>
        </div>
        <!-- Gateau -->
        <div class="cat">
            <img src="./photos/gateau1.JPG" alt="Cat 1">
            <p>Gateau is all black cat. He likes sleeping.</p>
        </div>
        <!-- Add more cats as needed -->
    </div>
    <a href="index.html">Back to Main Page</a>
</body>
</html>

